  m_text: "<b>TH\xD4NG B\xC1O THANH TO\xC1N D\u1ECACH V\u1EE4 - TH\xC1NG 6</b><br>------------------------------------------<br><b>1.
    Ti\u1EC1n ph\xF2ng tr\u1ECD:</b> 3,000,000\u0111<br><b>2. Ti\u1EC1n \u0111i\u1EC7n
    (80kWh):</b> 280,000\u0111<br><b>3. Ti\u1EC1n n\u01B0\u1EDBc (3 kh\u1ED1i):</b>
    60,000\u0111<br><b>4. Ti\u1EC1n Internet:</b> 160,000\u0111<br>------------------------------------------<br><b>T\u1ED4NG
    C\u1ED8NG:</b> <color=#ff4d4d>3,500,000\u0111</color><br>H\u1EA1n ch\xF3t thanh
    to\xE1n: 15/06/2026.<br><br><i>L\u01B0u \xFD: Qu\xE1 h\u1EA1n s\u1EBD c\u1EAFt
    d\u1ECBch v\u1EE5 \u0111i\u1EC7n n\u01B0\u1EDBc v\xE0 thu h\u1ED3i ph\xF2ng tr\u1ECD.</i><br><i>T\xE0i
    kho\u1EA3n hi\u1EC7n t\u1EA1i: 500,000\u0111 (Thi\u1EBFu: 3,000,000\u0111).</i>"
